name: &aMystery Man Rescue
author: iCodeDreams
description: The Mystery Man has been captured by the police, you have to save him!
location: Speak to Pat and Jen in Noobville!

DialogStage.Pat: Oh no!
The Mystery Man has been caught by the police!
We need your help to save him!
The cops took him yesterday and we spotted them in Army Base.
Will you help?
DialogStage.[PLAYER]: Of course I will help!
DialogStage.Pat: Thank you!
Jen are you coming too?
Okay, great. I'll meet you at Army Base tomorrow at 9am.

ObjectiveStage: Find Pat and Jen in Army Base

DialogStage.Pat: Hey.
DialogStage.[PLAYER]: Hi. What are we going to do?
DialogStage.Jen: The Mystery Man is being interrogated. I think...
DialogStage.Pat: Yes, it looks like we need to go that way.
We need to get in there and get him back without them noticing.
DialogStage.[PLAYER]: How would we do that?
DialogStage.Pat: Here, I'll explain.
Jen, you can go back to Noobville
and make sure no police are watching the area.
DialogStage.Jen: Okay, I will be on the lookout.

DialogStage.Pat: Okay, [PLAYER]. Follow me!
DialogStage.[PLAYER]: Sure thing.

DialogStage.Pat: You see those 2 security guards by the door?
DialogStage.[PLAYER]: Yes, I do.
DialogStage.Pat: You can't get in without a police badge.
There is probably some badges lying around Army Base.
You should go try to find one, and then enter and help the Mystery Man.
I will be back in Noobville waiting for you along with Jen.
We believe in you!
DialogStage.[PLAYER]: But, wait! What is the rest of the plan...

ObjectiveStage: Find a Police Badge in Army Base
Show your Police Badge to the Security Guards

DialogStage.Christopher: Okay, thank you. You may go in.

DialogStage.[PLAYER]: Hello, can I have a word with you for one second?
DialogStage.Hudson: Sure thing, Sabrina keep watch over the Mystery Man!

DialogStage.[PLAYER]: This interrogation has gone no where.
We do not know for sure that he has been selling stones.
and there is no way to prove he is.
May I have a word with the Mystery Man now?
DialogStage.Hudson: I mean, you can try. You may have a word with him.
Sabrina you may stop watching the Mystery Man.
[PLAYER] is going to have a word with him.

DialogStage.[PLAYER]: Hey. Pat and Jen sent me to save you.
They didn't really tell me a plan to get you out of here though.
So, on the count of 3 we run.
RUN!!!

DialogStage.Hudson: Get them!

DialogStage.[PLAYER]: What!?!
Where am I?
DialogStage.Hudson: You can't just run off like that.
You think you can fool us like that?
Give me that badge!
You are not a police officer!
Did you really think they wouldn't catch you?
You are not going anywhere with that Mystery Man.
DialogStage.[PLAYER]: What do I have to do in order for you guys to let him free?

DialogStage.Hudson: Well, we don't really have evidence.
I guess we could let you all free.
But, I wont!
DialogStage.[PLAYER]: Please!
DialogStage.Hudson: Well, I guess I could let you all free if you beat all the police officers.
But, if we catch the Mystery Man selling stones...
He will go to jail.
DialogStage.[PLAYER]: Deal!
DialogStage.Mystery Man: Don't I get a say in this?
DialogStage.[PLAYER]: Do you WANT to go back to interrogation or something?

NpcBattleStage.Sabrina: Uh. Time to beat this little peasant.
You really think you have a chance?
The Mystery Man is gonna stay with us.
Well you may have beat me but you have to beat all of us!
Looks like you're not getting the Mystery Man anytime soon...

NpcBattleStage.Lauren: Uh. Time to beat this little peasant.
You really think you have a chance?
The Mystery Man is gonna stay with us.
Well you may have beat me but you have to beat all of us!
Looks like you're not getting the Mystery Man anytime soon...

NpcBattleStage.Arfelio: So. You beat 2 of our officers.
Well, you won't beat me though.
Wow. I did not expect that. Well you have more to go!
Come back when you have a chance...

NpcBattleStage.Tyler: I just got a new team.
Are you sure you want to fight me?
NpcBattleStage.[PLAYER]: The Mystery Man is gonna stay with us.

NpcBattleStage.Tyler: Wow! You beat my new team! I guess I have to get used to the team before I fight.
I knew you wouldn't be able to beat me.

DialogStage.Hudson: What!?!?
You beat all the officers?
DialogStage.[PLAYER]: Yes sir! Now let me and the Mystery Man go!
DialogStage.Hudson: Fine!
But if we find out the Mystery Man has been selling stones...
You both will be back here in a heartbeat!

ObjectiveStage: Head to Noobville and talk to Pat and Jen

DialogStage.Pat: Now the Mystery Man can go back to selling stones!
But, Mystery Man be careful and don't get caught.
DialogStage.Mystery Man: I won't. But, They took the stones I had when they brought me to Army Base.
They said, it's just a precaution in case you are selling them.
I can't sell stones if I don't have any...
[PLAYER]! Will you go back to Army Base and search for a basket of stones?
DialogStage.[PLAYER]: Sure thing!

ObjectiveStage: Head to Army Base and look for a Basket of Stones

DialogStage.Christopher: We will get you for this...

ObjectiveStage: Give the Basket of Stones to the Mystery Man

DialogStage.Pat: Yes, thank you.
Without you the whole server would be without stones for awhile!
So... Did you learn anything today?
DialogStage.[PLAYER]: Yes, never run from the police!
DialogStage.Pat: Good!
DialogStage.Jen: I knew you could do it!
Not a teeny-weeny little thought that you couldn't.
Now, I must repay you for helping us out!

DialogStage.Mystery Man: Now, how ever could I repay you?
DialogStage.[PLAYER]: Yes please!
DialogStage.Mystery Man: Sure thing. That is the least I could do for you.
Here, take a random stone out of the basket.

DialogStage.[PLAYER]: Thank you.
